\c 2
\s UNehemiya uvunyelwa ukuya eJerusalema
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi ngenyanga kaNisani\x + Esta 3.7.\x*, ngomnyaka wamatshumi amabili kaAthakisekisi inkosi\x + 1.1. Ezra 7.1.\x*, iwayini laliphambi kwakhe, ngaphakamisa iwayini nganika inkosi\x + 1.11.\x*. Njalo ngangingakaze ngidane phambi kwayo.
\v 2 Inkosi yasisithi kimi: Kungani ubuso bakho budanile lokhu ungaguli\x + Gen. 40.7.\x*? Kakusilutho ngaphandle kokudana kwenhliziyo. Ngasengisesaba kakhulukazi\x + Zaga 15.13.\x*,
\v 3 ngathi enkosini: Kayiphile inkosi kuze kube nininini\x + 1 Kho. 1.31.\x*! Ubuso bami bungedane ngani nxa umuzi, indawo yamangcwaba abobaba, ulunxiwa\x + 1.3.\x*, lamasango awo eqedwe ngomlilo\x + 2.13.\x*?
\v 4 Inkosi yasisithi kimi: Kuyini okudingayo? Ngasengikhuleka kuNkulunkulu wamazulu\x + 1.4,5. 2.20. Ezra 5.12. Dan. 2.18.\x*.
\v 5 Ngathi enkosini: Uba kukuhle enkosini, njalo uba inceku yakho ithole umusa phambi kwakho, \add ngicela\add* ukuthi ungithume koJuda emzini wamangcwaba abobaba, ukuze ngiwakhe.
\v 6 Inkosi yasisithi kimi, lendlovukazi ihlezi eceleni kwayo: Uhambo lwakho luzakuba ngolwesikhathi esingakanani, ubuye nini? Ngakho kwaba kuhle phambi kwenkosi ukuthi ingithume; ngasengiyinika isikhathi esimisiweyo\x + 5.14. 13.6.\x*.
\v 7 Ngasengisithi enkosini: Uba kulungile enkosini kayinginike izincwadi eziya kubabusi bangaphetsheya komfula ukuze bangivumele ukudlula, ngize ngifike koJuda\x + Ezra 8.36. 1 Kho. 10.15.\x*;
\v 8 lencwadi eya kuAsafi, umphathi wegusu inkosi elalo\x + Tshu. 2.5.\x*, ukuthi anginike izigodo zokwenza imigubazi yamasango lesigodlo esiseduze lendlu, lezomduli womuzi\x + 7.2. 1 Lan. 29.1.\x*, lezendlu engizangena kiyo\x + 3.7.\x*. Inkosi yanginika njengokwesandla esihle sikaNkulunkulu wami phezu kwami\x + 2.18. Ezra 7.6.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Ngasengifika kubabusi ngaphetsheya komfula, ngabanika incwadi zenkosi\x + Ezra 8.36. 1 Kho. 10.15.\x*. Inkosi yayithume-ke lami induna zebutho labagadi bamabhiza.
\v 10 Lapho uSanibhalathi\x + 2.19. 4.1,7. 6.1,2,5,12,14. 13.28.\x* umHoroni\x + Isa. 15.5. Jer. 48.3,5,34. Josh. 10.11.\x* loTobiya inceku\x + 2.19. 4.3,7. 6.1,12,14,17,19. 13.4,7,8.\x*, umAmoni\x + 1 Sam. 11.1.\x*, besizwa, kwabacunula ngokucunula okukhulu ukuthi umuntu ufikile ukudingela abantwana bakoIsrayeli okuhle\x + Esta 10.3.\x*.
\v 11 Ngafika-ke eJerusalema, ngaba lapho insuku ezintathu.
\s UNehemiya ukhuthaza abeJerusalema ukwakha imiduli yomuzi
\p
\v 12 Ngasengisukuma ebusuku, mina lamadoda amalutshwana elami; kangitshelanga muntu lokho uNkulunkulu wami ayekufake enhliziyweni yami ukuthi ngikwenzele iJerusalema. Futhi kwakungelanyamazana kanye lami ngaphandle kwenyamazana engangiyigadile\x + Ezra 8.32.\x*.
\v 13 Ngasengiphuma ebusuku ngesango lesigodi, ngaqonda emthonjeni womgobho\x + 2 Lan. 26.9.\x* lesangweni lomquba\x + 3.13,14. 12.31.\x*, ngihlola imiduli yeJerusalema eyayidilikile\x + 1.3.\x* lamasango ayo ayeqedwe ngomlilo\x + 2.3.\x*.
\v 14 Ngasengisedlulela esangweni lomthombo\x + 3.15. 12.37.\x* lechibini lenkosi\x + 3.16. 2 Kho. 20.20. 2 Lan. 32.3,30.\x*; kodwa kwakungelandawo yenyamazana ukwedlula ngaphansi kwami.
\v 15 Ngasengisenyuka ngesifula ebusuku ngihlola umduli\x + 2 Sam. 15.23.\x*; ngaphenduka, ngangena ngesango lesigodi\x + 2 Lan. 26.9.\x*, ngabuyela.
\v 16 Lababusi babengazi lapho engangiye khona lokuthi ngenzani. Kuze kube khathesi-ke ngangingatshelanga amaJuda labapristi leziphathamandla\x + Ezra 9.2.\x* lezinduna labanye ababesenza umsebenzi\x + Ezra 9.2.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Ngasengisithi kibo: Liyabona inhlupheko esikiyo ukuthi iJerusalema ilunxiwa\x + 2.3.\x* lamasango ayo atshiswe ngomlilo\x + 1.3.\x*. Wozani sakhe umduli weJerusalema ukuze singabe sisaba lihlazo\x + 1.3. Hlab. 44.13. 79.4. Jer. 24.9. Hez. 5.14,15. 22.4.\x*.
\v 18 Ngasengibatshela isandla sikaNkulunkulu wami esasisihle phezu kwami, futhi lamazwi enkosi eyayiwakhulume kimi. Basebesithi: Asisukumeni, sakhe\x + 2.8.\x*. Ngakho baqinisa izandla zabo ngokuhle\x + 2 Sam. 2.7.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Lapho uSanibhalathi umHoroni loTobiya inceku, umAmoni, loGeshema umArabhiya\x + 6.1,2,6. 4.7.\x* besizwa basihleka usulu, baseyisa\x + 4.1. Hlab. 80.6. Hlab. 44.13. 79.4.\x* bathi: Iyini linto eliyenzayo? Liyayivukela inkosi yini\x + 6.6.\x*?
\v 20 Ngasengibabuyisela impendulo ngathi kibo: UNkulunkulu wamazulu yena uzasiphumelelisa; lathi inceku zakhe sizasukuma sakhe; kodwa lina kalilasabelo lelungelo lesikhumbuzo eJerusalema\x + Ezra 4.3.\x*.
